snippet.title: LET IT DIE - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
LET IT DIE is LIVE 12/3/2016.

Officially announced as part of the PlayStation Experience showcase,  LET IT DIE is exclusively available on the PlayStation 4. 

Download the free to play mayhem today!

#letitdiethegame #DIEtoSURVIVE
